OL,3,CNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,4,Cstressed over school holidays, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,8,Ffeel financial and emotional pressure
OL,9,Fduring school summer holidays, new
OL,10,Fresearch shows.
OL,12,FA report by Save the Children Cymru
OL,13,Ffound that 89% of parents in Wales
OL,14,Fthink the school summer break
OL,15,Fincreases pressure on families, with
OL,16,Fover half saying it is the most
OL,17,Fchallenging holiday of the year ahead
OL,18,Fof Christmas.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
