OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784740728
OL,3,CNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,4,Cstressed over school holidays, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOne in five parents in Wales also say
OL,8,Fthey struggle to buy essentials such
OL,9,Fas suncream and hats, as well as being
OL,10,Funable to provide the same summer
OL,11,Fexperience for their child as they had
OL,12,Fwhen they were younger.
OL,14,FThe findings comes from a survey taken
OL,15,Fby two thousand parents in the UK who
OL,16,Fhave at least one child aged 16 or
OL,17,Funder, with 211 participants based in
OL,18,FWales.
OL,20,FMelanie Simmonds, Head of Save the
OL,21,FChildren Cymru, said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
