OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784740728
OL,3,CNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,4,Cstressed over school holidays, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Our survey shows that cost of living
OL,8,Fpressure is continuing to squeeze
OL,9,Ffamily budgets across Wales.
OL,11,F"While many families are finding it
OL,12,Fharder to make ends meet, those on the
OL,13,Flowest incomes are facing the greatest
OL,14,Fchallenges, with no summer break from
OL,15,Fpoverty.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
