OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784740728
OL,3,CNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,4,Cstressed over school holidays, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"But there is opportunity going
OL,8,Fforwards to begin to address this
OL,9,Fthrough the Welsh Government's plans
OL,10,Fto pilot a Welsh Child Payment. This
OL,11,Fpayment would be a powerful lever to
OL,12,Faddress child poverty and give
OL,13,Ffamilies the support they need to
OL,14,Fensure children have the childhood
OL,15,Fthey deserve."
OL,17,FIn a statement, The Welsh Government
OL,18,Fsaid:
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
