CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784740728
OL,3,CNearly nine in ten parents in Wales
OL,4,Cstressed over school holidays, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"We are committed to tackling child
OL,8,Fpoverty in Wales and recognise the
OL,9,Fpressures many families face,
OL,10,Fparticularly during school holidays.
OL,12,F"We are helping with the cost of
OL,13,Fliving through the expansion of funded
OL,14,Fchildcare, support for local
OL,15,Fauthorities to improve holiday
OL,16,Fchildcare provision, and investment in
OL,17,Fholiday childcare and play
OL,18,Fopportunities across Wales.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
